rows.label: qst300406_msg001
rows.name: 神獣戦艦の入り口で艦長とトーク

rows.label: qst300406_msg0002
rows.name:
A Jeweled Signet?
Nothing of that sort around here,
I assure you.

rows.label: qst300406_msg0003
rows.name:
Now, if you will excuse me, we are
quite busy here with preparations to
depart. I would ask you to kindly leave.

rows.label: qst300406_msg0101
rows.name:
Companions of the Special Inquisitor
though you may be, this is hardly a
place for civilians to loiter.
